// Forge Platform — AdapterService gRPC service definition
//
// This is the contract between hub and spoke sidecars. The hub runs
// an AdapterServiceServicer (Python gRPC server). Spoke sidecars call
// these RPCs to register, stream data, and receive commands.
//
// Architecture:
//   Spoke Sidecar ──gRPC──► Hub Server
//     (TS/Python)            (Python)
